zed unidentified species (Sparassidae), subadult male, opposite embankment of Amazon River, Cumaceba Lodge, Loreto, Peru. Photograph: © W. Lamar, Tyler, Texas, United States." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4309251" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4309251/files/figure.png" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
, Pereira 2018)
